Global setup:

 Set up git
  git config --global user.name "tmeits"
  git config --global user.email tmeits@gmail.com
        

Next steps:

  mkdir tmeits.github.com
  cd tmeits.github.com
  git init
  touch README
  git add README
  git commit -m 'first commit'
  git remote add origin git@github.com:tmeits/tmeits.github.com.git
  git push -u origin master
      

Existing Git Repo?

  cd existing_git_repo
  git remote add origin git@github.com:tmeits/tmeits.github.com.git
  git push -u origin master
      

